#1. Create a greeting for your program.
title = print("Do you want a suggestion for your band name?")

#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.
City = input("\n1 - What's the name your hometown?\nans = ")

#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.
Pet = input("\n2 - tell me pet's name, maybe of a favorite one of yours.\nans = ")

#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print("\nSo a good name for your band would be...\n\n\n\n\n        ...\n        ...\n        ...\n\n\n\n" +         Pet, City)

